  Image Policy

   I love it when you love my work! You may use any of my photos or
   recipes from a post you enjoy here to be featured on your site, as long
   as you provide a link back to me and notify me either in the comments
   or with a direct email. It may not be accompanied by the project
   tutorial, whether in my own words as it originally appears or
   paraphrased. I do not permit photos of my family to be shared without
   my express written consent for each photo used. I know that by
   publishing on the internet, anyone can see what I share, but it’s still
   my intellectual property and it only belongs here at The Crafting Nook
   by TitiCrafty. Thanks for playing fair and respecting my copyright!

